    ZERO SUM COMPRESSION: Can we avoid enumerating zeros?
    ======================================================================
    
    --- Smooth zero sum approximation of π(x) ---
    Replacing discrete sum over zeros with integral against smooth N'(T)
    
      n=   50, x=    229: π_smooth(x)=50.2101, error=0.2101, time=1.17s
