    | 2025 | Arithmetic terms for Mersenne/Fermat/twin prime counting | Prunescu, Shunia |
    | 2025 | Arithmetic terms for smallest/largest prime divisor | Prunescu, Shunia |
    | 2025 | Arithmetic terms for GCD | Prunescu, Shunia |
    
    ### 8.2 What Prunescu-Shunia Actually Achieved
    
    They gave the FIRST explicit arithmetic terms for pi(n) and p(n). Before their
    work, Mazzanti's theorem guaranteed existence but nobody had written one down.
    
    The construction uses:
