    ## Experiment 1: Walsh-Hadamard Period Finding on Prime Gaps
    
    **Idea:** Quantum Fourier Transform finds hidden periodicities in O(polylog(N)). Classical FFT does it in O(N log N). If prime gaps have exploitable quasi-periodic structure (from zeta zeros), extract it.
    
