    | Universe N = p(10^100) | ~10^102 |
    | Number of primes pi(N) | ~4.3 x 10^99 |
    | Prime density 1/ln(N) | ~1/235 |
    | Binary entropy H(p) | 0.0397 bits/position |
    | **Minimum storage** | **~10^100.6 bits = ~10^99.7 bytes** |
    | Atoms in universe | ~10^80 |
