## Session 7 Complete — Summary

**205+ approaches tested across 7 sessions, 53+ sub-agents.**

### This Session's Work
- **8 background sub-agents**: internet search, interactive proofs, diophantine/algebraic, compressed sensing, recursive decomposition, novel paradigms, quantum approaches, succinct data structures
- **8 direct experiments**: modular CRT, generating functions, gap recurrences, fractal structure, prime race narrowing, additive construction, ultimate approaches, series acceleration
