### The Barrier Stands
After 205+ approaches, the O(x^{2/3}) classical barrier (O(x^{1/3}) quantum) is confirmed from every angle in mathematics and computer science. The best working solution remains **v10** (C-accelerated Lucy DP + Newton bisection, 100% exact, p(10^9) in 0.175s).
