    # Session 9 Results: Precomputation + Interpolation Attack
    
    **Date**: 2026-04-04  
    **Approach**: Can precomputation at strategic checkpoints + interpolation yield O(polylog) exact p(n)?  
    **Code**: `interpolation_attack.py`
    
    ---
    
    ## Executive Summary
    
    All five precomputation + interpolation strategies fail to break the barrier. Each approach ultimately reduces to the same obstruction: **~170 bits of irreducible information per prime near p(10^100)** cannot be generated without counting primes, regardless of how many checkpoints are precomputed.
    
